::Feline::

She watched him leave.  She waited for him to be of her sight before 
moving again.  She walked over and picked up the parts off the 
ground.  She then walked down the hall and into the CR chamber room.  
She walked to her repair area and startd fixing up the boards and 
took apart the arms.  She could parts from the arms in both arms or 
legs to repair the bots when they came in.  She tried to get things 
set up and ready.
